description: This Chainlink VRF top 2% rating Parvati purrs with a rating of 82, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 82, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, Box for East, 5 for South, and 2 for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40821-64522-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [82 Votes, Top 2% Rating]
